Search Examples:

  • To list all education institutions in NSW that have UNIVERSITY in their NAME:
    • Click on the Reset button to reset the form;
    • Select New South Wales (NSW) from the State drop-down list-box;
    • Type: UNIVERSITY in the Institution Name text box; and
    • Click on the Start Search button to commence the search.

  • To display details of the education institution with an CRICOS Institution Code of 00120C:
    • Click on the Reset button to reset the form;
    • Type: 00120C in the CRICOS Institution Code text box; and
    • Click on the Start Search button to commence the search.
